ZH: 豆腐是一种用豆类榨出的食品。
EN: Tofu is a food made by pressing soybeans.

ZH: 我喜欢在煎饼里加一些豆腐。
EN: I like to add some tofu to my pancakes.

ZH: 豆腐含有丰富的蛋白质。
EN: Tofu is rich in protein.

ZH: 姐姐做豆腐汤的手艺非常好。
EN: My sister is very good at making tofu soup.

ZH: 豆腐在中国菜肴中很常见。
EN: Tofu is commonly used in Chinese dishes.

ZH: 你知道怎么制作软豆腐吗？
EN: Do you know how to make soft tofu?

ZH: 昨天晚上我吃了一块烤豆腐。
EN: I had a piece of grilled tofu last night.

ZH: 豆腐有很多不同的种类。
EN: There are many different types of tofu.

ZH: 他们家的豆腐非常好吃。
EN: Their tofu is very delicious.

ZH: 豆腐是素食主义者的最爱。
EN: Tofu is a favorite among vegetarians.

ZH: 我经常把豆腐加入沙拉里。
EN: I often add tofu to my salads.

ZH: 请给我一些嫩豆腐。
EN: Please give me some soft tofu.

ZH: 豆腐炒鸡蛋是我的最爱。
EN: Stir-fried tofu with eggs is my favorite.

ZH: 他们家的麻婆豆腐很有名。
EN: Their mapo tofu is well-known.

ZH: 我不太喜欢吃冷冻豆腐。
EN: I don't really like frozen tofu.

ZH: 饭馆里的豆腐鱼味道很正宗。
EN: The tofu fish in the restaurant tastes authentic.

ZH: 这个火锅里有很多豆腐和蔬菜。
EN: This hotpot has a lot of tofu and vegetables.

ZH: 豆腐包含丰富的矿物质。
EN: Tofu is rich in minerals.

ZH: 我妈妈的辣豆腐饭最好吃。
EN: My mom makes the best spicy tofu rice.

ZH: 请给我一份素炒豆腐。
EN: I'll have a vegetarian stir-fried tofu, please.
